{"tid":2046833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星国《聯合早報》漫畫影射川普「雙重標準」","createTime":"2020-06-01T16:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T01:07:11.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6fc0d2072b3338971e304212e931e9a16bcd3543","tid":2046833,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T16:10:01.000Z","msg":"香港近期因「港版國安法」爆發動亂；美國也因「佛洛伊德之死」造成國內示威活動蔓延。新加坡聯合早報的特約漫畫家王錦松，在1日發布了一篇漫畫，直指美國總統川普對於這兩起事件持雙重標準，看待香港示威行動稱為「民主」，而當面對自身國內的動亂，卻又以「暴徒」稱呼這些示威者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202006/20200601/Cartoon20200536.jpg?itok=gXxR5ex3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zaobao.com.sg%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Farticle_large_full%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F202006%2F20200601%2FCartoon20200536.jpg%3Fitok%3DgXxR5ex3&h=26ac1f37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n王錦松是新加坡漫畫家，以繪畫時事漫畫著名，曾得過國際時事漫畫獎，目前為新加坡聯合早報特約漫畫家。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200601/1727677.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200601%2F1727677.htm&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns81lsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=4c7315fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200601/1727677.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b277429bc5d78d5ef37d2ca67a90471230b40851","tid":2046833,"uid":17103,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T16:16:35.000Z","msg":"用得簡體個腦係咪都小緊忽？"},{"pid":"5b828485916446cc6a5fa83e20ffd54815b7d83c","tid":2046833,"uid":25468,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T16:16:54.000Z","msg":"呢個擺明支那底，坡佬恨不得香港俾美國制裁啦，條友係坡奸"},{"pid":"2e9148e2cc5f2f458aa03354f38a8cdcbee2caec","tid":2046833,"uid":308251,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T16:19:22.000Z","msg":"中國新加坡市"},{"pid":"311f2ef0cbb7bae42ac331e7ac77dbab265dba4b","tid":2046833,"uid":191812,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T16:19:35.00